&lt;h2&gt;Fluent Builder (Modern Variation)&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;fluent-builder-modern-variation&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#fluent-builder-modern-variation&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The fluent builder is a modern variation that improves readability by returning the builder instance (this) from each method. This allows multiple build steps to be chained together in a single expression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Characteristics&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;characteristics-1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
