&lt;li&gt;Builder methods return the builder itself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enables method chaining&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Emphasizes readability and developer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Example Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;example-usage-1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
